description: The ATX NTR aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Austrian blue chip companies listed in EUR on the Vienna Stock Exchange (Wiener Borse) 20 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, largest component is capped at 20% Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.wienerborse.at
name: Xtrackers ATX UCITS ETF 1C
